```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph Docker["Docker"]
        Airflow[Airflow Scheduler<br/>Orchestrator]
        Connector["Bluesky Connector<br/>(AT Protocol's search API)"]
        Cleaner["Text Cleaning<br/>(strip URLs, emojis)"]
        Scorer["Sentiment Scoring<br/> Hugging Face <br/> Transformer"]
        UI[Streamlit Dashboard]
        DB[("PostgreSQL")]
    end

    %% Airflow orchestration (dashed lines)
    Airflow -.->|schedules (hourly/daily)| Connector
    Airflow -.->|triggers after Connector| Cleaner
    Airflow -.->|triggers after Cleaner| Scorer

    %% Data flow (solid lines)
    Connector -->|stores raw posts| DB
    DB -->|sends raw data| Cleaner
    Cleaner -->|stores cleaned posts| DB
    DB -->|sends clean data| Scorer
    Scorer -->|stores sentiment scores| DB

    %% UI reads from database
    DB -->|reads data| UI
```
